e of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思，ant<javac>中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 16:55:19','2013-10-12 08:55:19','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=198',0,'revision','',0),(199,1,'2013-10-12 16:57:07','2013-10-12 08:57:07','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<p/>\r\n下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=“_blank”>详见原文</a>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<p/>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong>\r\n<p/>\r\n带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=“_blank”>详见原文</a>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p/>\r\n上面说的意思，ant<javac>中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 16:57:07','2013-10-12 08:57:07','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=199',0,'revision','',0),(200,1,'2013-10-12 17:00:03','2013-10-12 09:00:03','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\"></pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:00:03','2013-10-12 09:00:03','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=200',0,'revision','',0),(201,1,'2013-10-12 17:00:20','2013-10-12 09:00:20','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br/>\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\"></pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:00:20','2013-10-12 09:00:20','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=201',0,'revision','',0),(202,1,'2013-10-12 17:00:47','2013-10-12 09:00:47','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\"></pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:00:47','2013-10-12 09:00:47','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=202',0,'revision','',0),(203,1,'2013-10-12 17:01:22','2013-10-12 09:01:22','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\