l be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\"></pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:01:22','2013-10-12 09:01:22','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=203',0,'revision','',0),(204,1,'2013-10-12 17:02:37','2013-10-12 09:02:37','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加，也可以省略。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:02:37','2013-10-12 09:02:37','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=204',0,'revision','',0),(205,1,'2013-10-12 17:04:44','2013-10-12 09:04:44','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。\r\n<h3>像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加也可省略。</h3>\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\"></pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:04:44','2013-10-12 09:04:44','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=205',0,'revision','',0),(206,1,'2013-10-12 17:05:33','2013-10-12 09:05:33','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加也可省略。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:05:33','2013-10-12 09:05:33','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=206',0,'revision','',0),(207,1,'2013-10-12 17:07:29','2013-10-12 09:07:29','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table class=\"alignleft\" style=\"border-color: #d4d7d5; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 550px; height: 160px;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加也可省略。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:07:29','2013-10-12 09:07:29','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=207',0,'revision','',0),(208,1,'2013-10-12 17:11:55','2013-10-12 09:11:55','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加也可省略。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:11:55','2013-10-12 09:11:55','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=208',0,'revision','',0),(209,1,'2013-10-12 17:12:22','2013-10-12 09:12:22','使用ant编译源代码后部署的java应用，在遇到错误或异常时都会遇到这种情况，控制台打印的堆栈信息看不到行号，取而代之的是<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">unknow source</span>，如下列所示：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-159\" alt=\"unknowsource\" src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/unknowsource.png\" width=\"514\" height=\"127\" /></a>\r\n\r\n另外在使用ant集成findbugs及checkstyle等代码质量检查工具时，一般都会遇到经过检查的警告或者错误无法定位到行问题，这些问题都是因为ant&lt;javac&gt;任务参数设置导致的，其实归根结底都是javac -g参数设置的问题，下面我逐步给大家解释，并告诉如何解决此问题。\r\n<h3>下面是我从javac命令官方文档中摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/technotes/tools/solaris/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<blockquote><b>javac</b> [ options ] [ sourcefiles ] [ classes ] [ @argfiles ]\r\n...\r\n<strong>-g</strong>\r\nGenerate all debugging information, including local variables. By default, only line number and source file information is generated.\r\n<strong>-g:none</strong>\r\nDo not generate any debugging information.\r\n<strong>-g:{keyword list}</strong>\r\nGenerate only some kinds of debugging information, specified by a comma separated list of keywords. Valid keywords are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>source  Source file debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lines Line number debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>vars Local variable debugging information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n...</blockquote>\r\n上面说的意思我们使用javac命令会默认带-g参数，它就是用来生成调试信息，不过只会生成源代码行号及源文件调试信息，使用-g:none关闭所有调试信息，使用-g:{source,lines,vars}(这三个可以任选)可以打开{}中包含项对应的调试信息。\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">看到上面这个解释你可能就奇怪了，javac既然默认打开行号调试信息，那为什么ant?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>带着这个问题，我们去查查ant关于javac的文档，下面是我从ant官方文档摘录的一部分内容，<a href=\"http://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/javac.html\" target=\"“_blank”\">详见原文</a></h3>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Attribute</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Description</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Required</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debug</td>\r\n<td>Indicates whether source should be compiled with debug information; defaults to <code>off</code>. If set to <code>off</code>, <code>-g:none</code> will be passed on the command line for compilers that support it (for other compilers, no command line argument will be used). If set to <code>true</code>, the value of the <code>debuglevel</code> attribute determines the command line argument.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>debuglevel</td>\r\n<td>Keyword list to be appended to the <code>-g</code> command-line switch. This will be ignored by all implementations except <code>modern</code>, <code>classic(ver &gt;= 1.2)</code> and <code>jikes</code>. Legal values are <code>none</code> or a comma-separated list of the following keywords: <code>lines</code>, <code>vars</code>, and <code>source</code>. If <code>debuglevel</code> is not specified, by default, nothing will be appended to <code>-g</code>. If <code>debug</code> is not turned on, this attribute will be ignored.</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n上面说的意思，ant中debug参数默认是off，这样对应生成执行的命令javac -g:none，这种情况编译后的字节码文件不带有调试信息，这下真相大白了吧，至于debuglevel参数我就不介绍了。像下面这样修改ant的build.xml文件中javac参数debug,debuglevel根据需要添加也可省略。\r\n<pre lang=\"xml\" line=\"1\">\r\n<javac ...\r\n    debug=\"true\" debuglevel=\"source,lines\">  \r\n</javac>\r\n</pre>','[原创]ant <javac> Unknow source','','inherit','open','open','','157-revision-v1','','','2013-10-12 17:12:22','2013-10-12 09:12:22','',157,'http://blog.me/?p=209',0,'revision','',0),(211,1,'2013-10-21 11:26:26','2013-10-21 03:26:26','<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">转载地址：</span><a href=\"http://hi.baidu.com/chrisfoon/item/a53d6d2758889ec9ddf69a56\">http://hi.baidu.com/chrisfoon/item/a53d6d2758889ec9ddf69a56</a>\r\n\r\n需要安装 lzo 和 lzop\r\n\r\n一、lzo 安装\r\n\r\n1. 下载lzo文件\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# wget http://www.oberhumer.com/opensource/lzo/download/lzo-2.06.tar.gz\r\n</pre>\r\n2. 编译安装\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# tar xzvf lzo-2.06.tar.gz\r\n[root@localhost ~]# cd lzo-2.06\r\n[root@localhost lzo-2.06]# ./configure --enable-shared\r\n[root@localhost lzo-2.06]# make\r\n[root@localhost lzo-2.06]# make install\r\n</pre>\r\n3. 复制lib\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# cp /usr/local/lib/*lzo* /usr/lib64/\r\n[root@localhost ~]# cp /usr/local/lib/*lzo* /usr/lib/\r\n</pre>\r\n二、lzop安装\r\n\r\n1. 下载lzop包\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# wget \'http://www.lzop.org/download/lzop-1.03.tar.gz\'\r\n</pre>\r\n2. 编译安装\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# tar xzvf lzop-1.03.tar.gz\r\n[root@localhost ~]# cd lzop-1.03\r\n[root@localhost lzop-1.03]# ./configure\r\n[root@localhost lzop-1.03]# make\r\n[root@localhost lzop-1.03]#make install\r\n</pre>\r\n如果lzop提示找不到命令，尝试执行：\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]#ln -s /usr/local/bin/lzop /usr/bin/lzop\r\n</pre>\r\n三、测试\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# lzop -V\r\n</pre>\r\n结果如下：\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lzop-v.png\"><img src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lzop-v.png\" alt=\"lzop-v\" width=\"718\" height=\"149\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215\" /></a>\r\n\r\n命令使用帮助：\r\n<pre lang=\"bash\">\r\n[root@localhost ~]# lzop -h\r\n</pre>\r\n结果如下：\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lzop-h.png\"><img src=\"http://blog.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lzop-h.png\" alt=\"lzop-h\" width=\"709\" height=\"580\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" /></a>\r\n\r\n测试压缩文件：\r\n[gateway@localhost home]$ time lzop tianqitong_20130130.log\r\n\r\nreal 0m7.429s\r\n\r\nuser 0m5.260s\r\n\r\nsys 0m1.100s\r\n\r\n485M tianqitong_20130130.log.lzo','[转载]Linux 安装lzop压缩工具','','publish','open','open','','%e8%bd%ac%e8%bd%bdlinux-%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85lzop%e5%8e%8b%e7%bc%a9%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7','','','2013-10-21 11:26:26','2013-10-21 03:26:26','',0,'http://blog.me/?p=211',0,'post','',0),(212,1,'2013-10-21 11:14:09','2013-10-21 03:14:09','<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">转载地址：</span><a href=\"http://hi.baidu.com/chrisfoon/item/a53d6d2758889ec9ddf6